<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Fire Nation Attacks</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="mainHeader d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <h1>Fire Nation Attacks!</h1>
</div>

<p>Fire Nation ships have reached to the shore. <br>
    Prince Zuko is approaching to Team Avatar slowly... </p>

<div class="hero mainHeader d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <h2>Team Avatar has something to say!</h2>
    <form action="/quotes" method="POST">
        <input type="text" placeholder="character name" name="name"/>
        <input type="text" placeholder="quote" name="quote"/>
        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>

    <h2 class="pt-4">Quotes</h2>

    <div class="quotes">
        <ul class="list-unstyled quotes">
            <% for(var i = 0; i < quotes.length; i++) { %>
                <li class="quote">
                    <span class="quotation"><%= quotes[i].name %></span>:
                    <span class="quotation">"<%= quotes[i].quote %>"</span>
                </li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="buttons row m-0">

    <div class="d-flex flex-column col-6 align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="headline-left d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"><h2 class="headlines">Facing Zuko Once Again!</h2></div>
        <p>Press the button to taunt the Avatar. This action will replace quotes! </br> This button only works when
            there are quotes from Team Avatar
            (humans) on the screen.</p>
        <form action="/zuko" method="POST">
            <button type='submit' id="update-button">"I must capture the Avatar!"</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex flex-column col-6 align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="headline-right d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"><h2 class=''>Zuko is out of control!</h2></div>
        <p>Press the button to calm Zuko down. This action will delete Zuko@s quotes! </br>This button only works when
            there are quotes from Zuko on the
            screen.</p>
        <button id="delete-button">"If we knew each other back then...</br>Do you think we could have been friends too?"
        </button>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"><span id="message" class="span"></span></div>
<script src="/main.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"><span class="span">Su Jade, 2024 </br>
        Brush vectors from Vecteezy.com</span></div>

</body>
</html>